OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fgreyer for Friday evening with some
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain moving across the
OL,8,Fregion overnight. Drier again by dawn
OL,9,Fbut skies remaining rather cloudy for
OL,10,Fmany with hill fog. A mild night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA grey start in places, but
OL,13,Fthe cloud breaking and lifting during
OL,14,Fthe morning. Somewhat brighter skies
OL,15,Ffor the afternoon, though sunshine
OL,16,Foften hazy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
