OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry and settled throughout
OL,7,Fthe bank holiday weekend and into next
OL,8,Fweek with plenty of sunshine. Feeling
OL,9,Fvery warm by day with potentially some
OL,10,Fwarm nights too.
